gpm_dep.description: JSON is a light-weight, language independent, data interchange format.See http://www.JSON.org/The files in this package implement JSON encoders/decoders in Java.It also includes the capability to convert between JSON and XML, HTTPheaders, Cookies, and CDL.This is a reference implementation. There are a large number of JSON packagesin Java. Perhaps someday the Java community will standardize on one. Untilthen, choose carefully.
